## PAGE TEMPLATES\
\
### Module Overview Page \'97 Information Architecture\
\
1. **Header banner** \'97 module number, title, branded gradient\
2. **Context bar** \'97 week number, time estimates (synchronous / asynchronous)\
3. **Learning objectives** \'97 "In this module you will:" with action verbs (Bloom's taxonomy)\
4. **Key topics** \'97 concise topic list, light background\
5. **Start Here block** \'97 dark background, major deliverable and due date\
6. **What to Expect This Week** \'97 collapsible panel with synchronous/asynchronous breakdown\
7. **Contact footer** \'97 instructor email + office hours link\
\
### Assignment Page \'97 Information Architecture\
\
1. **Header banner** \'97 assignment name, module context\
2. **Purpose statement** \'97 why this assignment matters (1\'962 sentences)\
3. **Learning objectives** \'97 what the student demonstrates\
4. **Instructions** \'97 numbered steps or clear prose\
5. **Deliverables** \'97 what to submit, format requirements\
6. **Evaluation criteria** \'97 rubric summary or link to full rubric (modal or tab)\
7. **Due date and submission** \'97 prominent, unambiguous\
\
### Discussion Page \'97 Information Architecture\
\
1. **Header banner** \'97 discussion title, module context\
2. **Prompt** \'97 the question or scenario\
3. **Requirements** \'97 post length, reply expectations, deadlines\
4. **Evaluation criteria** \'97 how participation is graded\
\
### Quiz Page \'97 Information Architecture\
\
1. **Header banner** \'97 quiz title, module context\
2. **Purpose statement** \'97 what knowledge or skills are being assessed\
3. **Preparation guidance** \'97 what to review before attempting (link to relevant content)\
4. **Quiz parameters** \'97 number of questions, time limit, attempts allowed, availability window\
5. **What to expect** \'97 question types, whether questions are shuffled, backtracking allowed\
6. **After submission** \'97 when and how results are available\
\
### Home / Start Page \'97 Information Architecture\
\
1. **Welcome banner** \'97 course title, instructor, term\
2. **Course overview** \'97 positioning statement (2\'963 sentences)\
3. **Navigation** \'97 module list or link grid to all modules\
4. **Quick links** \'97 syllabus, schedule, key resources\
5. **Contact footer** \'97 instructor email + office hours\
